# Secrets and credentials
# Nothing in this repo should ever contain real credentials.
# Use Windows Credential Manager (preferred) or environment variables.

# GitHub PAT (for the OpenClaw `manager` helper, not committed here)
# Google app password (Jimothy's Gmail)
# OpenAI API key (for GPT-4o calls — Will's handwriting)

# Indexed paper KVdb bucket ids
# These are *public*, not secrets — anyone with the URL can read or write
# to a KVdb bucket. That's fine for our use; the bucket ids are stored in
# papers/<name>/kvdb-bucket.txt after indexing.

# Local-only paths and per-paper extracted text
papers/*/extracted.txt
papers/*/paper.json
papers/*/markscheme.json
papers/*/kvdb-bucket.txt

# Per-batch photo transcripts (rebuildable from intake/photos)
transcripts/

# Generated assessment output (rebuildable)
assessments/

# Generated HTML for Pages (rebuildable)
pages/assessments/

# Email outbox (rebuildable)
outbox/

# Standard Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.env
.venv/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Intentionally NOT ignored: papers/*.pdf, intake/*/photos, index/papers.json,
# calibration/*.md, src/, prompts/. These are the actual data.
